songs.title: Adavi Chetla Naduma
songs.lyrics:
Adavi Chetla Naduma 
 Oka Jaldaru Vruksham Vale 
 Parishuddula Samaajamulo 
 Yesu Prajvalinchuchunnaadu (2) 
KeerthinthunNaaPrabhuni
JeevaKaalamellaPrabhuYesuni
KruthagnathathoSthuthinchedanu(2)
